🎧 Mood-Based Music Recommendation System
A full-stack web application that detects a user's mood using facial expressions and recommends music accordingly using AI and YouTube integration.
---
🚀 Features
🎥 Real-time mood detection using webcam
🤖 Emotion recognition using DeepFace
🎵 Mood-based YouTube music recommendations
🖥️ Simple and interactive UI
🔘 Manual mood selection option
---
🛠️ Technologies Used
Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend:** Python (Flask)
Libraries:** DeepFace, OpenCV, Requests
Tools:** VS Code, GitHub
