⚙️ Installation & Setup
1. Clone the repository:
```
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/mood-music-recommender.git
```
2. Navigate to the project folder:
```
cd mood-music-recommender
```
3. Install dependencies:
```
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
4. Run the Flask app:
```
python app.py
```
5. Open in browser:
```
http://127.0.0.1:5000/
```
---
🎯 How It Works
1. User opens the web application
2. Webcam captures facial image
3. DeepFace analyzes emotion
4. System detects mood (happy, sad, angry, etc.)
5. Corresponding YouTube playlist is recommended
